    "en": {
      "title": "Three were caught selling brass balls that had been sprinkled from the king's basket",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Welikada police arrested three suspects who were preparing to sell 40 golden brass balls that were stolen while they were attached to the walls to hang curtains.",
        "Yesterday afternoon (24th), these suspects were brought to a market selling old goods in Welikada Obeysekarapura area and according to the information received in this regard, the three were arrested.",
        "Police also mention that the suspects are drug addicts residing in Obeysekarapura area."
      ],
